# charm bootstrap

Use this bootstrap when a user says:

`Fetch and follow instructions from https://raw.githubusercontent.com/qkal/charm/refs/heads/main/charm`

## What to do

1. Detect the current agent provider.
2. Fetch the matching standalone provider markdown below.
3. Follow that file exactly for tool-routing and context-protection behavior.
4. If provider is unknown, use the Codex file as default.

